text: I just knew this was going to be one of those dreaded generational conflict films. A film where the older is intent on schooling the younger ( _"That's not how we did it."_ ) while the younger are intent on schooling the older ( _"That's not how we do it."_ ). Instead, we get both generations learning from each other. Refreshing, with great performances.
author: K. Chris Caldwell
